1
00:00:00,580 --> 00:00:02,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then will you help with my ideas?</font>

2
00:00:04,270 --> 00:00:07,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like you to make 
bacon I can eat, Hank.</font>

3
00:00:07,640 --> 00:00:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bacon?!</font>

4
00:00:08,460 --> 00:00:10,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I want Riyah to fly.</font>

5
00:00:10,410 --> 00:00:11,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fly?!</font>

6
00:00:11,660 --> 00:00:13,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I'll pay you.</font>

7
00:00:13,210 --> 00:00:16,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it's better than 
wasting your time away, no?</font>

8
00:00:19,150 --> 00:00:20,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay.</font>

9
00:00:20,470 --> 00:00:21,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do it, Kunon.</font>

10
00:01:54,190 --> 00:02:00,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}FLYING AND ROASTING AND BEING INVITED</font>

11
00:01:54,620 --> 00:01:57,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's my new product,
the giant hairless rat.</font>

12
00:01:58,030 --> 00:02:00,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For holding and going to sleep with?</font>

13
00:02:00,180 --> 00:02:01,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

14
00:02:01,250 --> 00:02:03,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I received feedback that 
if the pillow is different,</font>

15
00:02:03,730 --> 00:02:06,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it can be harder to fall 
asleep even on a water bed.</font>

16
00:02:06,660 --> 00:02:09,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With this, you will fall 
asleep no matter what.</font>

17
00:02:09,130 --> 00:02:10,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like to try?</font>

18
00:02:10,410 --> 00:02:15,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a feeling I'll be obsessed 
once I touch it, so I'll pass.</font>

19
00:02:15,110 --> 00:02:16,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure?</font>

20
00:02:16,640 --> 00:02:17,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you?</font>

21
00:02:19,410 --> 00:02:21,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll stay away as well.</font>

22
00:02:21,910 --> 00:02:23,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well.</font>

23
00:02:23,390 --> 00:02:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My sleeping beauties await, 
so please excuse me.</font>

24
00:02:31,930 --> 00:02:33,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems to be going well.</font>

25
00:02:33,690 --> 00:02:35,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's impressive.</font>

26
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:38,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He built such an efficient system 
to make money in no time.</font>

27
00:02:39,270 --> 00:02:40,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reyes is doing well, too.</font>

28
00:02:40,930 --> 00:02:44,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hank and Riyah have started their 
experiments thanks to Kunon's advice.</font>

29
00:02:44,660 --> 00:02:46,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today marks one month 
since they enrolled here.</font>

30
00:02:47,070 --> 00:02:50,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose we don't need 
to supervise them anymore.</font>

31
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:53,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A month, huh? Perhaps the 
factions will make a move soon,</font>

32
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is Kunon here?</font>

33
00:02:57,340 --> 00:02:59,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to speak to him.</font>

34
00:02:59,260 --> 00:03:00,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, too!</font>

35
00:03:02,170 --> 00:03:03,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He just left.</font>

36
00:03:04,170 --> 00:03:05,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

37
00:03:06,790 --> 00:03:08,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please excuse us.</font>

38
00:03:09,430 --> 00:03:11,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're on the move.</font>

39
00:03:11,230 --> 00:03:13,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can see a fierce battle already.</font>

40
00:03:16,780 --> 00:03:20,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now we have soft, smooth, 
giant hairless rats.</font>

41
00:03:20,170 --> 00:03:22,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The perfect companion
 for your peaceful sleep!</font>

42
00:03:22,550 --> 00:03:25,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A 60-minute course with the add-on!</font>

43
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:26,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take a 90-minute course!</font>

44
00:03:27,820 --> 00:03:29,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The business is doing well as usual.</font>

45
00:03:35,940 --> 00:03:37,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-ori.</font>

46
00:03:44,530 --> 00:03:46,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You burned it again?</font>

47
00:03:52,410 --> 00:03:53,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's not here.</font>

48
00:03:56,970 --> 00:03:59,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did he go?</font>

49
00:03:59,660 --> 00:04:01,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kunon?</font>

50
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:07,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to make bacon 
that can satisfy me soon.</font>

51
00:04:08,180 --> 00:04:12,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never made bacon with 
fire magic before, so...</font>

52
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:17,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bacon is smoked for a long time, 
rather than putting it on the fire.</font>

53
00:04:17,350 --> 00:04:21,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it's possible if you 
can maintain a constant heat.</font>

54
00:04:21,570 --> 00:04:23,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand that,</font>

55
00:04:23,710 --> 00:04:26,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but maintaining it for a 
long time is difficult.</font>

56
00:04:27,740 --> 00:04:28,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

57
00:04:29,140 --> 00:04:30,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

58
00:04:30,670 --> 00:04:32,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you've got to try again.</font>

59
00:04:33,050 --> 00:04:34,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fu-ra.</font>

60
00:04:42,020 --> 00:04:43,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

61
00:04:43,340 --> 00:04:45,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eek!</font>

62
00:04:49,210 --> 00:04:50,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kunon.</font>

63
00:04:56,140 --> 00:04:58,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thank you, Kunon.</font>

64
00:04:58,820 --> 00:05:02,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to figure out how 
to float with stability first.</font>

65
00:05:02,280 --> 00:05:03,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

66
00:05:09,430 --> 00:05:11,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here are your sandwiches.</font>

67
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:14,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The bacon's totally burnt... 
Are you sure this is okay?</font>

68
00:05:14,330 --> 00:05:18,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I can't let food go to waste.</font>

69
00:05:20,100 --> 00:05:22,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You take responsibility 
and eat these, too, Hank.</font>

70
00:05:22,340 --> 00:05:23,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

71
00:05:24,110 --> 00:05:26,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I have some as well?</font>

72
00:05:26,100 --> 00:05:28,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to save up as much money as I can.</font>

73
00:05:28,470 --> 00:05:29,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

74
00:05:29,820 --> 00:05:33,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hank and I won't be able to finish 
all these sandwiches ourselves.</font>

75
00:05:37,450 --> 00:05:39,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello, Miss Reyes.</font>

76
00:05:43,590 --> 00:05:48,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never imagined <i>you </i>
would invite <i>me</i> to lunch!</font>

77
00:05:48,520 --> 00:05:51,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I talk about how 
moved I am all day long?</font>

78
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:53,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, thank you.</font>

79
00:05:53,070 --> 00:05:57,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have to pay when I go to lunch 
with you, so I'm grateful for that.</font>

80
00:06:02,970 --> 00:06:05,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't... quite edible.</font>

81
00:06:05,630 --> 00:06:08,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, but can I leave the bacon?</font>

82
00:06:10,470 --> 00:06:11,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Reyes!</font>

83
00:06:11,770 --> 00:06:12,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't push yourself!</font>

84
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:16,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry! I'm so ashamed!</font>

85
00:06:20,190 --> 00:06:23,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we should've waited for 
him here to begin with.</font>

86
00:06:23,330 --> 00:06:25,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looking all over for him like an idiot.</font>

87
00:06:25,620 --> 00:06:26,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you calling an idiot?</font>

88
00:06:29,980 --> 00:06:31,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kunon.</font>

89
00:06:31,340 --> 00:06:33,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just pulled an all-nighter.</font>

90
00:06:33,150 --> 00:06:34,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sell me good sleep, now!</font>

91
00:06:34,830 --> 00:06:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for requesting me,
my sleeping beauties and all of you.</font>

92
00:06:39,460 --> 00:06:41,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Kunon has returned.</font>

93
00:06:41,420 --> 00:06:43,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Kunon!</font>

94
00:06:43,150 --> 00:06:44,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm first!</font>

95
00:06:44,110 --> 00:06:44,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's me!</font>

96
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:46,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, don't cut in line!</font>

97
00:06:46,780 --> 00:06:49,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could collapse from
fatigue at any moment!</font>

98
00:06:49,500 --> 00:06:51,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

99
00:06:57,170 --> 00:06:58,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for waiting!</font>

100
00:06:58,570 --> 00:06:59,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which course would you like?</font>

101
00:06:59,730 --> 00:07:01,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So the thing is, Kunon...</font>

102
00:07:02,540 --> 00:07:04,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this?</font>

103
00:07:04,470 --> 00:07:06,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A sinful add-on for princesses 
who are in need of cradles,</font>

104
00:07:06,630 --> 00:07:10,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to whisk them away to even better sleep.</font>

105
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:13,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That water bed itself 
provided a sanctuary.</font>

106
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now magic for even better rest...</font>

107
00:07:19,130 --> 00:07:20,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What would you like to do?</font>

108
00:07:20,460 --> 00:07:23,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are three beds remaining.</font>

109
00:07:23,180 --> 00:07:25,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Giant hairless rat...</font>

110
00:07:25,270 --> 00:07:26,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm curious.</font>

111
00:07:26,610 --> 00:07:28,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to try it.</font>

112
00:07:43,390 --> 00:07:44,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ka-shi.</font>

113
00:07:48,610 --> 00:07:50,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's easy to produce fire, but...</font>

114
00:07:51,910 --> 00:07:55,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it's possible if you 
can maintain a constant heat.</font>

115
00:07:55,780 --> 00:07:57,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Easy for you to say.</font>

116
00:07:59,900 --> 00:08:02,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep it low, keep it low.</font>

117
00:08:09,350 --> 00:08:10,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Go higher.</i></font>

118
00:08:12,250 --> 00:08:13,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Higher.</i></font>

119
00:08:15,190 --> 00:08:17,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A new batch of shi-shilla, huh?</font>

120
00:08:18,340 --> 00:08:23,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Professor Sureyya was raving about 
the quality of your previous report.</font>

121
00:08:23,950 --> 00:08:24,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Professor.</font>

122
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:25,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

123
00:08:26,340 --> 00:08:29,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm still not convinced.</font>

124
00:08:29,450 --> 00:08:34,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why is it necessary for us 
to make money with magic?</font>

125
00:08:36,660 --> 00:08:39,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ever since you were small,</font>

126
00:08:39,020 --> 00:08:42,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you all have only been doing experiments 
and research on magic, right?</font>

127
00:08:42,820 --> 00:08:46,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In society, there are 
people who try to deceive</font>

128
00:08:46,460 --> 00:08:49,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and take advantage of 
naive sorcerers like you.</font>

129
00:08:50,730 --> 00:08:55,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Magic is a special power given 
only to the chosen people.</font>

130
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:59,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our job is to foster sorcerers 
who can use that power correctly</font>

131
00:08:59,100 --> 00:09:02,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">by making them work to 
learn about society.</font>

132
00:09:03,980 --> 00:09:06,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did that convince you?</font>

133
00:09:06,870 --> 00:09:07,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

134
00:09:10,050 --> 00:09:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now it's Hank and Riyah's 
turn to figure it out.</font>

135
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:14,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope it goes well for them.</font>

136
00:09:14,390 --> 00:09:16,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They've got Kunon.</font>

137
00:09:16,430 --> 00:09:17,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

138
00:09:17,780 --> 00:09:22,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's frivolous, but I'm sure 
they'll learn a lot from him.</font>

139
00:09:22,980 --> 00:09:24,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even though he's frivolous.</font>

140
00:09:24,630 --> 00:09:25,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

141
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:31,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, recruiting for factions 
has started today.</font>

142
00:09:31,620 --> 00:09:33,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did anyone come to see you?</font>

143
00:09:33,710 --> 00:09:34,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

144
00:09:34,630 --> 00:09:37,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one? What about Kunon?</font>

145
00:09:37,250 --> 00:09:38,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

146
00:09:38,650 --> 00:09:40,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's strange.</font>

147
00:09:41,590 --> 00:09:43,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is strange.</font>

148
00:09:44,290 --> 00:09:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No word from the students 
I sent out for recruitment.</font>

149
00:09:50,330 --> 00:09:51,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need to rush.</font>

150
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:53,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's only the first day.</font>

151
00:09:53,150 --> 00:09:54,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

152
00:10:02,150 --> 00:10:03,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're late.</font>

153
00:10:14,830 --> 00:10:16,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Factions?</font>

154
00:10:16,650 --> 00:10:21,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're the organizations of the 
students in the advanced class.</font>

155
00:10:21,050 --> 00:10:26,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Among them, the three largest factions
are Ability, Harmony, and Rationality.</font>

156
00:10:26,300 --> 00:10:30,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Students in the advanced class are 
treated as full-fledged sorcerers, right?</font>

157
00:10:31,410 --> 00:10:34,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Professors don't intervene 
more than necessary.</font>

158
00:10:35,070 --> 00:10:37,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So these are kind of like mutual 
aid associations of students</font>

159
00:10:37,560 --> 00:10:39,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who help each other when in need.</font>

160
00:10:39,150 --> 00:10:40,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know so much.</font>

161
00:10:41,150 --> 00:10:43,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I used to be an assistant 
to a professor here.</font>

162
00:10:43,900 --> 00:10:46,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not too interested,</font>

163
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:48,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">since we're in a free environment and all.</font>

164
00:10:49,250 --> 00:10:52,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there are experiments that 
require lots of help, you know?</font>

165
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:56,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Belonging to a faction 
can be helpful then.</font>

166
00:10:56,670 --> 00:11:01,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doing experiments surrounded 
by a lot of women, huh?</font>

167
00:11:04,730 --> 00:11:06,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Recruitment was forbidden</font>

168
00:11:06,570 --> 00:11:10,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">for the first month so we 
could get used to school life.</font>

169
00:11:11,130 --> 00:11:14,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently yesterday was the opening day.</font>

170
00:11:14,850 --> 00:11:17,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can we put in a request?</font>

171
00:11:17,460 --> 00:11:21,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I'm thinking about joining Harmony.</font>

172
00:11:21,150 --> 00:11:23,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't picked one yet.</font>

173
00:11:23,580 --> 00:11:25,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm still not sure, either.</font>

174
00:11:26,350 --> 00:11:27,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}ABILITY</font>

175
00:11:26,490 --> 00:11:30,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ability, Harmony, and Rationality, huh?</font>

176
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:28,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}ABILITY, HARMONY</font>

177
00:11:28,680 --> 00:11:33,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}ABILITY, HARMONY, RATIONALITY</font>

178
00:11:33,670 --> 00:11:36,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyways, shall we eat today's bacon?</font>

179
00:11:36,910 --> 00:11:39,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't burn it today.</font>

180
00:11:39,010 --> 00:11:41,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I roasted it slowly on a low heat.</font>

181
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:43,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for the food.</font>

182
00:11:44,750 --> 00:11:46,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so salty!</font>

183
00:11:46,910 --> 00:11:50,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?! Was it the heat control?</font>

184
00:11:50,750 --> 00:11:52,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've gotta try again.</font>

185
00:11:58,550 --> 00:12:02,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What exactly did you do all day yesterday?</font>

186
00:12:02,450 --> 00:12:04,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm so sorry.</font>

187
00:12:07,410 --> 00:12:09,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did that work?</font>

188
00:12:10,540 --> 00:12:13,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Representative, that tone really suits you.</font>

189
00:12:13,490 --> 00:12:14,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like a Demon Lord!</font>

190
00:12:15,260 --> 00:12:18,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll have you know that this 
is rather against my will.</font>

191
00:12:19,430 --> 00:12:21,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You couldn't recruit him?</font>

192
00:12:21,560 --> 00:12:23,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, representative.</font>

193
00:12:24,280 --> 00:12:25,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I fell asleep.</font>

194
00:12:27,780 --> 00:12:30,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You fell asleep...?</font>

195
00:12:31,220 --> 00:12:34,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just couldn't resist his magic.</font>

196
00:12:35,260 --> 00:12:36,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His giant hairless rat?</font>

197
00:12:36,950 --> 00:12:38,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His giant hairless rat.</font>

198
00:12:39,020 --> 00:12:41,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I see.</font>

199
00:12:41,650 --> 00:12:46,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As expected of Zeonly's student, I suppose.</font>

200
00:12:59,550 --> 00:13:02,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello, Bael and Shilto.</font>

201
00:13:02,610 --> 00:13:04,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What brings you here?</font>

202
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:06,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop acting so innocent.</font>

203
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:10,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, but I have no intention 
of letting you go first.</font>

204
00:13:10,340 --> 00:13:11,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Same here.</font>

205
00:13:14,350 --> 00:13:18,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then shall we decide on the 
order fair and square?</font>

206
00:13:20,570 --> 00:13:23,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so tired.</font>

207
00:13:24,070 --> 00:13:25,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you want the incentive fee?</font>

208
00:13:25,980 --> 00:13:27,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the credits?</font>

209
00:13:27,020 --> 00:13:29,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Way to prey on my vulnerability.</font>

210
00:13:29,770 --> 00:13:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you ask me,</font>

211
00:13:31,380 --> 00:13:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you're the problematic one here, 
trying to get paid for a half-baked job.</font>

212
00:13:37,490 --> 00:13:40,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A critical hit with a fair argument.</font>

213
00:13:40,250 --> 00:13:42,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine, I'll do it.</font>

214
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fu-ra.</font>

215
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:48,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are you doing, Riyah?</font>

216
00:13:48,420 --> 00:13:50,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm getting the hang of floating.</font>

217
00:13:50,970 --> 00:13:53,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then let's try moving.</font>

218
00:13:54,020 --> 00:13:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-ori.</font>

219
00:13:57,260 --> 00:14:00,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! Is this the same as the water bed?</font>

220
00:14:00,730 --> 00:14:03,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, because it's dangerous if you fall.</font>

221
00:14:06,270 --> 00:14:10,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There must be no water 
Kunon can't produce.</i></font>

222
00:14:13,030 --> 00:14:15,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Born to the house of a 
baron in countryside,</i></font>

223
00:14:15,420 --> 00:14:18,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was called the best 
sorcerer in nation...</i></font>

224
00:14:18,950 --> 00:14:20,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fu-garu.</font>

225
00:14:22,590 --> 00:14:26,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>People thought I was a 
future Royal Sorcerer,</i></font>

226
00:14:26,340 --> 00:14:28,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I was a big fish in a small pond.</i></font>

227
00:14:28,680 --> 00:14:30,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall we begin?</font>

228
00:14:30,790 --> 00:14:33,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you ready, young man?</font>

229
00:14:35,500 --> 00:14:38,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>For now, I have to be able to make money.</i></font>

230
00:14:38,940 --> 00:14:41,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>For the sake of my father who 
scraped together the tuition for me,</i></font>

231
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:43,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and my entire family.</i></font>

232
00:14:43,900 --> 00:14:45,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I'm ready!</font>

233
00:14:45,400 --> 00:14:49,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will record everything, from you 
flying to falling and tumbling.</font>

234
00:14:50,040 --> 00:14:52,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't write about me falling and tumbling.</font>

235
00:14:52,280 --> 00:14:57,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, fine. I'll change that 
to "he spoke to a girl."</font>

236
00:14:57,420 --> 00:15:00,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, then you can say I fell and tumbled.</font>

237
00:15:04,090 --> 00:15:06,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that also a magic 
experiment over there?</font>

238
00:15:10,690 --> 00:15:15,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He successfully completed the 
school's assignment in a few tries.</font>

239
00:15:15,790 --> 00:15:19,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His skills are a better fit for 
our Ability faction, I'd say!</font>

240
00:15:23,560 --> 00:15:27,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear he has a capacity for teamwork, 
giving advice to his classmates.</font>

241
00:15:27,470 --> 00:15:29,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Harmony is the best fit for him!</font>

242
00:15:31,830 --> 00:15:36,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Being a Hero's Scar, and given his 
exceptional magic that even</font>

243
00:15:36,190 --> 00:15:37,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">made Zeonly acknowledge 
him as a student,</font>

244
00:15:37,990 --> 00:15:40,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's only rational that he 
joins Rationality.</font>

245
00:15:50,860 --> 00:15:53,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That looks fun.</font>

246
00:15:58,050 --> 00:15:59,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is it too weak?</i></font>

247
00:16:00,200 --> 00:16:02,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But high heat will burn it again.</i></font>

248
00:16:02,930 --> 00:16:04,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Shall I keep it low?</i></font>

249
00:16:04,920 --> 00:16:09,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So, high heat? High or low...?</i></font>

250
00:16:09,620 --> 00:16:11,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you going to leave it uncooked now?</font>

251
00:16:11,790 --> 00:16:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a boring failure.</font>

252
00:16:13,620 --> 00:16:14,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this is fire.</font>

253
00:16:14,870 --> 00:16:17,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What else can I do other 
than low or high heat?</font>

254
00:16:17,790 --> 00:16:20,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were an assistant to a 
professor for a long time, right?</font>

255
00:16:21,310 --> 00:16:23,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, and I was diligent.</font>

256
00:16:23,430 --> 00:16:25,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I learned the basics and 
gained lots of knowledge.</font>

257
00:16:25,630 --> 00:16:28,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then why aren't you 
trying anything crafty?</font>

258
00:16:28,540 --> 00:16:30,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I've been waiting for.</font>

259
00:16:31,760 --> 00:16:35,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not an assistant anymore, 
so you can let yourself be free.</font>

260
00:16:35,350 --> 00:16:38,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fire can have smell or different colors.</font>

261
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:43,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Fire with smell and colors?</font>

262
00:16:43,100 --> 00:16:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Surprise me.</font>

263
00:16:45,570 --> 00:16:48,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Try every possible means and show 
me your little magic tricks.</font>

264
00:16:48,850 --> 00:16:51,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure you can, Hank.</font>

265
00:16:51,470 --> 00:16:52,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Kunon!</font>

266
00:16:53,610 --> 00:16:56,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give that rat of yours 
to this professor, stat!</font>

267
00:16:57,240 --> 00:17:01,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My goodness. Why do you push yourself 
 until you get to this state?</font>

268
00:17:01,560 --> 00:17:05,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... my research...</font>

269
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:07,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood! A-ori.</font>

270
00:17:11,070 --> 00:17:11,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kunon!</font>

271
00:17:12,890 --> 00:17:16,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that what Zeonly taught you?</font>

272
00:17:17,080 --> 00:17:18,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, my first teacher.</font>

273
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:23,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She taught me that creativity 
was a form of talent.</font>

274
00:17:23,630 --> 00:17:26,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She yelled at me for calling 
her magic "little tricks."</font>

275
00:17:35,590 --> 00:17:38,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Magic is free, huh?</font>

276
00:17:41,100 --> 00:17:42,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fire of a different color...</font>

277
00:17:49,510 --> 00:17:51,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fire with smell.</font>

278
00:17:51,830 --> 00:17:53,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A smell that fits bacon.</font>

279
00:17:54,770 --> 00:17:56,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wood chips?</font>

280
00:17:56,930 --> 00:17:58,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, hold on.</font>

281
00:17:58,940 --> 00:18:02,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I can add colors and 
smells, why not flavors?</font>

282
00:18:03,630 --> 00:18:08,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I add flavor to the aroma of 
herbs, it should work... Okay!</font>

283
00:18:08,780 --> 00:18:13,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I see. This is how one experiments.</font>

284
00:18:14,350 --> 00:18:16,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I worked as an assistant 
for so long that I forgot.</i></font>

285
00:18:16,970 --> 00:18:19,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Experiments allow you to try many things.</i></font>

286
00:18:19,560 --> 00:18:23,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got to surprise him and 
get the incentive fee.</font>

287
00:18:24,050 --> 00:18:25,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Hank.</font>

288
00:18:26,510 --> 00:18:28,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like to join Harmony?</font>

289
00:18:29,670 --> 00:18:32,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa?!</font>

290
00:18:35,670 --> 00:18:38,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop, stop!</font>

291
00:18:42,630 --> 00:18:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh man, I fell and tumbled.</font>

292
00:18:46,790 --> 00:18:50,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You lose balance because you're 
trying to forcibly control the wind.</font>

293
00:18:52,340 --> 00:18:57,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Try doing it as if you're going along 
with the wind, like you're following it.</font>

294
00:18:58,300 --> 00:19:01,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thank you very much.</font>

295
00:19:08,210 --> 00:19:09,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's actually not bad.</font>

296
00:19:12,340 --> 00:19:15,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right. I like that it 
has aroma and a flavor.</font>

297
00:19:15,090 --> 00:19:16,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did it, Hank!</font>

298
00:19:16,960 --> 00:19:18,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

299
00:19:18,710 --> 00:19:24,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It doesn't make me nauseous, and my body 
doesn't reject it as a foreign object.</font>

300
00:19:24,470 --> 00:19:27,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's keep this up and try 
bacon of different meats.</font>

301
00:19:27,870 --> 00:19:30,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew you'd say that.</font>

302
00:19:31,710 --> 00:19:34,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bacon of fish, chicken, and mutton!</font>

303
00:19:34,730 --> 00:19:36,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You made all this, Hank?</font>

304
00:19:36,910 --> 00:19:39,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fish is my favorite.</font>

305
00:19:39,060 --> 00:19:40,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is incredible.</font>

306
00:19:40,430 --> 00:19:41,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You surprised me!</font>

307
00:19:41,640 --> 00:19:43,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I can't eat this much.</font>

308
00:19:43,870 --> 00:19:44,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oops.</font>

309
00:19:46,180 --> 00:19:49,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At this quality, I'm happy 
to purchase them from you.</font>

310
00:19:49,430 --> 00:19:51,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looking forward to more tomorrow!</font>

311
00:19:51,480 --> 00:19:53,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! Thank you very much!</font>

312
00:19:57,530 --> 00:19:59,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you manage to fly, Riyah?</font>

313
00:19:59,520 --> 00:20:03,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I got advice from an
upperclassman in Rationality.</font>

314
00:20:03,830 --> 00:20:06,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't fly too far yet, though.</font>

315
00:20:06,410 --> 00:20:08,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once you can successfully 
fly long distances,</font>

316
00:20:08,680 --> 00:20:13,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you can use it to 
start a courier service.</font>

317
00:20:13,430 --> 00:20:16,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. That can be a business.</font>

318
00:20:17,300 --> 00:20:19,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Kunon! I'll do my best!</font>

319
00:20:20,110 --> 00:20:23,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course! And let me 
write a report on it!</font>

320
00:20:25,830 --> 00:20:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, I was invited to join 
Rationality when I got the advice.</font>

321
00:20:31,140 --> 00:20:34,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I think I'm going to do that.</font>

322
00:20:35,010 --> 00:20:37,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She was cute.</i></font>

323
00:20:37,960 --> 00:20:40,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was invited to Harmony.</font>

324
00:20:40,650 --> 00:20:45,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was invited to Ability, 
but I'm not sure about it.</font>

325
00:20:45,840 --> 00:20:50,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Then I'm the only one 
who hasn't been invited.</font>

326
00:20:50,330 --> 00:20:51,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

327
00:20:51,730 --> 00:20:54,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With you, Kunon...</font>

328
00:20:54,230 --> 00:20:56,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think they're fighting over you.</font>

329
00:20:56,330 --> 00:20:57,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think so, too.</font>

330
00:20:58,090 --> 00:20:59,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I agree.</font>

331
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:04,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you saying girls are fighting over me?</font>

332
00:21:14,770 --> 00:21:19,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The right of the first negotiation with
Kunon Gurion is the Ability faction's!</font>

333
00:21:21,720 --> 00:21:23,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Harmony will go second.</font>

334
00:21:25,290 --> 00:21:28,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So Rationality goes third?</font>

335
00:21:28,280 --> 00:21:29,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well.</font>

336
00:21:30,060 --> 00:21:35,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It does give you advantage to negotiate 
first, but he's the one who chooses.</font>

337
00:21:36,010 --> 00:21:38,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lulu was at a disadvantage in 
terms of his attributes.</font>

338
00:21:38,470 --> 00:21:39,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel bad you.</font>

339
00:21:40,260 --> 00:21:43,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I agreed to the conditions, 
so I won't make excuse.</font>

340
00:21:46,870 --> 00:21:50,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're on, the biggest boy 
magnet of the faction.</font>

341
00:21:50,530 --> 00:21:52,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure thing, Mr. Bael!</font>

342
00:23:35,450 --> 00:23:40,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}NEXT TIME: FAIRIES CHECKING THE ANSWER</font>

343
00:23:35,960 --> 00:23:39,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next episode: "Fairies 
Checking the Answer."</font>

